            "extra_id": 0x61,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Reisenberg, Reisenberg... Hmm, it's really far..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x61,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "As Sir Julio said, I'd need to thoroughly prepare for such a long journey..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x61,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "It would likely take a long time... ...Wait? A long journey...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "...I got it!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "While I travel to Reisenberg for the exam, I can gather materials to make Plachta human..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1c,
            "expr_id": 0xc,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "That's it! That'll be way more efficient! Good thinking, me!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1e,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "It's a good idea, but... I probably wouldn't be able to come back to Kirchen Bell for a long time..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Now that I think about it, I've never been away from town for that long... I wonder if I can get by outside..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "...Uu, there's no point in worrying! At times like this, it's best to try talking to others!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Let's see, who would be best... Monika... Would be hard to talk to..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Then I guess Oskar, plus Sir Julio, seeing how he brought it all up..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2e,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Also, someone used to traveling... Like Logy. Yeah, I'll go and talk to them!"
        }
    ]
}